ou in a real estate transaction, whether you are buying or selling. Ultimately, I strive to provide you with excellent customer service.","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739699084_1777229.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexrojas.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alex","agentlastname":"Hanuszkiewicz","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/d9la9jrhv6fdd.cloudfront.net\/agentimages\/nophoto.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexh.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alex","agentlastname":"Dubovoy","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"<p>Born in Mexico City, Alex relocated to Miami at a young age, where he witnessed firsthand the remarkable evolution of the South Florida real estate landscape. With a Bachelor's degree from Babson College and professional experience at J.P. Morgan, Alex has honed his skills in client relations and entrepreneurship. Fluent in both English and Spanish, Alex is dedicated to offering tailored service to clients from various backgrounds. Whether assisting buyers or sellers, he approaches each transaction with integrity, professionalism, and an unwavering commitment to surpassing expectations. In his leisure time, Alex enjoys immersing himself in South Florida's rich cultural offerings, staying active outdoors, and cherishing moments with his family. Excited to be part of the EWM team, Alex looks forward to leveraging his expertise to help clients navigate this dynamic real estate market and achieve their investment and personal goals.<\/p>","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739699054_1778825.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexdubovoy.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alexander","agentlastname":"Haigney","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739698582_1777076.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexanderhaigney.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alexandra","agentlastname":"Silva","agenttitle":"REALTOR\u00ae","agentabout":"<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in;\">Meet Alexandra, a dynamic professional with over two decades of experience in banking, finance, and investment, fueled by a strong passion for real estate. With a career spanning from managing multi-million-dollar investment portfolios to shaping strategic financial decisions, Alexandra brings a wealth of knowledge and a unique perspective to the world of real estate.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in;\">As a former Vice President and Portfolio Manager at Pacific National Bank in Miami, Alexandra managed a $260 million investment portfolio, specializing in structured securities. Her proficiency extends far beyond portfolio management, delving into comprehensive financial analysis and strategic planning. Prior to her tenure at PNB, Alexandra honed her skills as a senior Financial Analyst at CERA, contributing to the success of the company by crafting financial profitability reports and managing substantial operational budgets.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in;\">With academic credentials from prestigious institutions including a Graduate Certificate of Special Studies from Harvard University and a Master of Science in Economics from Universidad Cat&oacute;lica, Alexandra's commitment to continuous learning is evident. She has further fortified her expertise through Series 7 and Certified Financial Planner (CFP) courses, alongside holding a Real Estate License in Florida and FIBA Broker\/Dealer AML Certification.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in;\">Fluent in Spanish and armed with a comprehensive skill set encompassing investment portfolio management, financial analysis, and client relationship management, Alexandra is poised to contribute to the dynamic growth of forward-thinking real estate organizations. Her history of success and commitment to excellence positions her as an invaluable asset in the exciting world of real estate sales.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Segoe UI',sans-serif; color: #374151; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in;\">Let Alexandra be your guide in unlocking the limitless potential of the real estate market. Connect with her today to embark on your journey towards property success.<\/span><\/p>","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739698785_1777278.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexandrasilva.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alexandra","agentlastname":"Hechtman","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739698587_1777095.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexandrahechtman.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alexey","agentlastname":"Blagoveshchenskiy","agenttitle":"Realtor\u00ae","agentabout":"Meet Alexey, a dynamic real estate agent with a passion for helping clients achieve their real estate goals. With a background in the hospitality industry, Alexey understands the importance of providing exceptional customer service and attention to detail. He has also worked as a senior paralegal at an immigration law firm specializing in EB-5 investment visas, providing him with a unique perspective on the real estate market. Alexey\u2019s expertise in investment visas allows him to assist international clients in navigating the complex legal requirements of investing in US properties. He prides himself on his ability to build lasting relationships with his clients and is committed to providing them with personalized service and expert guidance throughout the buying and selling process. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or a seasoned investor, Alexey is the agent you can trust to help you achieve your real estate goals.","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739699022_1776728.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexeyblagoveshchenskiy.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alexis","agentlastname":"Fuentes","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/d9la9jrhv6fdd.cloudfront.net\/agentimages\/nophoto.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alexisfuentes.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alfonso","agentlastname":"Gomez","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739698733_1776852.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/alfonsogomez.ewm.com"},{"agentfirstname":"Alicia Tarafa","agentlastname":"Gilbert","agenttitle":"Sales Associate","agentabout":"","agentphoto":"https:\/\/dtzulyujzhqiu.cloudfront.net\/berkshirehathawayhomeservicesewmrealty11930\/profiles\/1739698618_1776790.jpg","agentsubdomain":"https:\/\/aliciatarafagilbert.ewm.com"},{"agentf